casebody.data:
Anthony Dewayne DOYLE, petitioner,
v.
TEXAS. No. 13-9344 (13A963). Supreme Court of the United States March 27, 2014.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice SCALIA and by him referred to the Court *1583denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Texas denied.
